<html
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
    xml:lang="en"
    lang="en"
    metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
    i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-subscribers" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-bugs" />
</metal:rightportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <div metal:use-macro="context/@@launchpad_form/form" />

</div>

<metal:help fill-slot="help">
  <p>Use this page to edit the request's <strong>title</strong> or
    <strong>description</strong>. If you are not the user who posted the
    request, try to only do edits that clarify the request or describes it
    better.
  </p>

  <p>In distribution, you may want to set the
    <strong>source package</strong> to which this support request is related.
    This will help people familiar with that application find the request.
  </p>

  <p>You can use the <strong>status whiteboard</strong> to leave a transient
    note that will be displayed on the support request page.
  </p>

</metal:help>

</body>
</html>
